com.jgaap.gui.dnd
Class DnDManager

java.lang.Object
  com.jgaap.gui.dnd.DnDManager

public class DnDManager
extends java.lang.Object

This class is the single point of contact between the guiDriver (GUI backend) and all of the drag and drop functionality on the CanonicizeStepPanel. Any drag and drop code that will affect the backend has to come through here. No drag and drop components should interact directly with guiDriver. TODO: Update GUI after mass changes

Author:
Chuck Liddell
